;B[ps]LB[qs:1][rs:2][or:3][ps:4]C[Dia.1 Black is alive

If White jumps in at 2 then he is practically saying "just live Black."  Black just plays 2 and then when White plays 3, he just makes his second eye at 4.  This is too easy on Black.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

