;W[sr]LB[rs:1][sq:2][qs:3][ss:4][or:5][ps:6][sr:7]C[Dia.3 Correct / White takes first

Well let's try White 1.  We still are makinga Pae but the difference here is that White takes the Pae first.  This mean Black has to find a big enough Pae threat, not the other way around.  This is better for White.
